  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.sql.PreparedStatement, java.sql.Statement, java.sql.Wrapper
    public class FilteredPreparedStatement
extends FilteredStatement
implements java.sql.PreparedStatement
    Wrapper for a SQL PreparedStatement The wrapper forwards all methods to the wrapped prepared statement
